column5: Google Street View came through my neighbourhood last summer and my van happened to be in the driveway. Google blurred out the license plate and my OFC sticker!!! But it left my Jumla Fishing sticker for all the world to see!!!
That is funny.  They DIDNT blur out my plate....do I have grounds for a lawsuit????

Yea I was home for something or other, when they went past my house. I considered it window shopping for the thieves when they fist came out with this. Hey, here’s  a place with a Vette in the laneway and no garage; easy picking. Now that the pic’s are dated; I guess it’s not that big a deal; I still own the car but now it sits at the front of the laneway in front of the truck.  Dan.
